@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_thgask(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.35 + tmp + 0.57)) - wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.03)))
    v1 = (0.16 - wp.sin((v1 + 0.18 / v0 + 0.03)))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = 0.03
    tmp = wp.cos((0.92 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)))
    tmp = wp.abs((v0 / (v0 + 0.97 + tmp + 0.71)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp((v2 + 0.22 - tmp + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.78) - (v1 + 0.88 + v1 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
